# After School Lessons - Full Stack Application

## Project Overview

This is a full-stack web application that allows students and their parents to browse, search, and purchase after-school classes and activities. The application consists of:

- **Front-End**: Built with Vue.js 2.7, providing a responsive user interface for browsing lessons, managing shopping cart, and placing orders
- **Back-End**: Built with Express.js and Node.js, providing REST API endpoints for lesson management and order processing
- **Database**: MongoDB Atlas for storing lessons and orders data

## Features

- Browse and search after-school lessons
- Filter lessons by location, price range, and availability
- Sort lessons by various criteria (subject, location, price, spaces)
- Add lessons to shopping cart with real-time availability updates
- Manage cart quantities and review selections
- Submit orders with customer information
- Responsive design with modern UI styling

